messages.speech: Your credit score is on the low side of qualifying you for a mortgage, but that's okay. I talk to people in your situation every day and generally I recommend a credit report consultation with a credit sensei before we talk about interest rates and mortgage calculations. Once we're sure you'll qualify at a reasonable interest rate we can take a closer look at true mortgage costs.
